message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $14,000. I believe it offers significant value at this price, considering its worth to you.
I'm interested in the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $11,000. Would you be willing to meet me in the middle?
I understand your position, Bob. However, $11,000 is significantly below its value. How about we settle at $13,000?
I appreciate your willingness to compromise, but $13,000 is still a bit above my budget. Would you be willing to go down to $12,500?
